You freaks shouldn't feel threatened by us Gnomes.  Just because we are the images of perfection. <br>
<br>
Also your prisoners are only there because they want to be.  All gnomes have the ability to self gate back to the secret gnomish labs at will.<br>
<br>
<br>
Here is a good Gnomish trick to play on evil gnome haters. <br>
I had a shammy cast enlarge on me to make me as big as an ogre.  I stood at the zone line in the bizarre and as soon as people other than Gnomes zoned in I hit the following hot key.<br>
<br>
/cast 8 (O'Keils Embers) <br>
/say %r like you have ruined your own lands<br>
/say You'll Not Ruin mine<br>
/say Time to die %t<br>
<br>
Lol people freaked out.  Some ran up to attack and it took em a moment to get over their shock and laugh and some turned tail and zoned out and didn't come back.<br>
<br>
Yruc 53 Gnome Wizard<br>
We are going to take over the world.<br>
